these should be `m` in `svd_solve`:

```
795) svd_jacobi(&(Ax[0]), &(U[0]), &(V[0]), &(sing_vals[0]), n, n);
-->  svd_jacobi(&(Ax[0]), &(U[0]), &(V[0]), &(sing_vals[0]), m, n);

807) gemm(&(U[0]), n, n, trans, &(b[0]), n, 1, trans, &(x[0]), n, 1, trans, 'T');
-->  gemm(&(U[0]), n, m, trans, &(b[0]), m, 1, trans, &(x[0]), n, 1, trans, 'T');
```

